{"tid":1124792,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"嘉諾撒聖心書院學生校友good","createTime":"2019-04-25T08:55:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-25T09:11:03.000Z","uid":36494,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"6144925a490e7e1a83142c8f645e20d3befdd7ea","tid":1124792,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T08:55:27.000Z","msg":"而獲准押後判刑的陳淑莊，她的母校嘉諾撒聖心書院則有學生及舊生發起聯署支持陳淑莊。聯署指陳投入佔領中環運動是出於為香港爭取普選，理想崇高。聯署指出聖心一直教育學生成為未來領袖，因其校其中一個學社以「Emmeline Pankhurst」命名，而Pankhurst是曾因爭取女性投票權而多次入獄的著名英國女權領袖。<br />\n<br />\n聖心學生及舊生認為，不少校友均認同陳淑莊是一個對社會有擔當的人，並視她為榜樣，並讚揚陳竭誠為社會服務，表現了她有原則、正直的一面。聯署也為得悉陳腦部發現有腫瘤並需接受緊急手術感到痛心、祝願陳早日康復，並呼籲各校友聯署支持陳淑莊。"},{"pid":"1bb8a48d7bba9dbd439f7b663e5694b2b3541dba","tid":1124792,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T08:56:00.000Z","msg":"👍"},{"pid":"3f3dc7924d0791cfa23744497fffbba38b677446","tid":1124792,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":11,"score":-11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T09:03:50.000Z","msg":"最憎聖心妹，又串又懶係眾人皆醉我獨醒咁樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6deef38f08c7663d3c5c85c6f7186af9753ccd3e","tid":1124792,"uid":5523,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"3f3dc7924d0791cfa23744497fffbba38b677446","tid":1124792,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":11,"score":-11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T09:03:50.000Z","msg":"最憎聖心妹，又串又懶係眾人皆醉我獨醒咁樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T09:08:54.000Z","msg":"渣咪比人串<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28f07101785158bb560d6931fa57b127ef6b2793","tid":1124792,"uid":32511,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6deef38f08c7663d3c5c85c6f7186af9753ccd3e","tid":1124792,"uid":5523,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"3f3dc7924d0791cfa23744497fffbba38b677446","tid":1124792,"uid":32511,"like":0